summary: This document contains location data for a mobile number associated with an ITN case. It provides longitude and latitude coordinates along with a confidence level for the location estimate. The document emphasizes caution in using the location data for investigative purposes due to potential inaccuracies.
keyFacts: The mobile number was located on 2020-06-30.

The location data is sourced from various databases, which may affect accuracy.
